-- China May Have 310,000 Ton Cotton Deficit Before New Crop Comes To Market
-- Bloomberg News
-- 2010-04-27T03:15:26Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-04-27/china-may-have-310-000-ton-cotton-deficit-before-new-crop-comes-to-market.html

          
          
             China may have a 310,000 metric ton
cotton deficit before the new crop comes onto the market, the
State-owned Assets Supervision and Administration Commission
said, citing the China National Cotton Reserves Corp.  
          
          


  


        